'''NGC 2360'''，也稱為'''卡洛琳的星團'''<ref name="simbad">{{cite web
  | title=SIMBAD Astronomical Database
  | work=Results for NGC 2360
  | url=http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=NGC+2360
  | accessdate=2010-12-03
  | archive-date=2017-03-17
  | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317095851/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=NGC+2360
  | dead-url=no
  }}</ref>，是位於[[大犬座|大犬座]]的一個[[疏散星團|疏散星團]]。它是卡洛琳赫歇爾在1783年2月26日發現的<ref name=hoskin05>{{cite journal|last=Hoskin|first=Michael|date=2005|title=Caroline Herschel as observer|journal=[[Journal_for_the_History_of_Astronomy|Journal for the History of Astronomy]]|volume=36|issue=4|pages=373–406|url=http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?2005JHA....36..373H&data_type=PDF_HIGH&whole_paper=YES&type=PRINTER&filetype=.pdf|bibcode=2005JHA....36..373H|access-date=2020-09-26|archive-date=2020-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404162101/http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?2005JHA....36..373H&data_type=PDF_HIGH&whole_paper=YES&type=PRINTER&filetype=.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，她寫道："一個被擠壓在直徑0.5度，標致的漂亮"<ref name="o'meara"/>。她的筆記一直被忽略，直到她的哥哥[[威廉·赫歇爾|威廉·赫歇爾]]在1786年出版，包含1000個星雲和星團的目錄中，大家才知道她是發現<ref name=hoskin05/>。這個星團位在[[天狼增四|天狼增四]]（大犬座γ）的東方3.5度，[[食雙星|食雙星]][[大犬座R|大犬座R]]西北方1度之處；它聚合的[[視星等|視星等]]為7.2等<ref name="o'meara">{{cite book |title=The Caldwell Objects |first=Stephen James |last=O'Meara |publisher=Cambridge University Press |date=2002 |pages=231–33 |url=http://books.google.com.au/books?id=3Hg6YHgx9nAC&pg=PA233&lpg=PA233&dq=%22NGC+2360%22&source=bl&ots=6aHbIt5xw4&sig=90WnmUltWFZXKx3yQ3R3q25pCzU&hl=en&sa=X&ei=EC0lU9_fCoT5kAWFq4C4Bw&ved=0CHsQ6AEwDA#v=onepage&q=%22NGC%202360%22&f=false |isbn=978-0-521-82796-6 |access-date=2016-01-19 |archive-date=2014-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316111505/http://books.google.com.au/books?id=3Hg6YHgx9nAC&pg=PA233&lpg=PA233&dq=%22NGC+2360%22&source=bl&ots=6aHbIt5xw4&sig=90WnmUltWFZXKx3yQ3R3q25pCzU&hl=en&sa=X&ei=EC0lU9_fCoT5kAWFq4C4Bw&ved=0CHsQ6AEwDA#v=onepage&q=%22NGC%202360%22&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它的視直徑為13角分<ref name="seds">{{cite web
  | title=SEDS Online NGC Database
  | work=Results for NGC 2360
  | url=http://spider.seds.org/ngc/ngc.cgi?N2360
  | accessdate=2010-12-03
  | archive-date=2011-08-07
  | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110807054855/http://spider.seds.org/ngc/ngc.cgi?N2360
  | dead-url=no
  }}</ref>。在這個星團西側邊緣，5.5等的[[HD_56405|HD 56405]]與星團之間沒有關聯性<ref name="streicher">{{cite web  | last = Streicher  | first = Magda  | date = April 2006  | title = Caroline Herschel’s Deepsky Discoveries  | publisher = The Astronomical Society of Southern Africa  | work = Deepsky Delights  | url = http://www.mnassa.org.za/html/Dec2005/2005MNASSA..64..Dec..234.pdf  | pages = 234–36  | accessdate = 16 March 2014  | archive-date = 2014-03-16  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140316123554/http://www.mnassa.org.za/html/Dec2005/2005MNASSA..64..Dec..234.pdf  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>。

美國天文學家[[Olin_J._Eggen|Olin J. Eggen]]在1968年對星團進行調查，確認在這個星團視場 中，最亮的[[HD_56847|HD 56847]]，視星等8.96，只是躺在星團前方，並不是這個星團的成員。他也確認其中有1或2顆[[藍掉隊星|藍掉隊星]]<ref>{{cite journal |title = The Intermediate-Age Cluster NGC 2360 |author = Eggen, Olin J. |journal = The Astrophysical Journal |volume = 152 |pages = 83–87 |bibcode = 1968ApJ...152...83E |url = http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?1968ApJ...152...83E&data_type=PDF_HIGH&whole_paper=YES&type=PRINTER&filetype=.pdf |doi = 10.1086/149526 |access-date = 2020-09-26 |archive-date = 2017-02-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170226224305/http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?1968ApJ...152...83E&data_type=PDF_HIGH&whole_paper=YES&type=PRINTER&filetype=.pdf |dead-url = no }}</ref>。這種比周圍的恆星更熱和更亮的恆星，看上去也比較年輕，並且可能已經歷過吞噬掉伴星的階段<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.northwestern.edu/newscenter/stories/2011/10/blue-stragglers.html|title=Astronomers Explain 'Blue Stragglers'|last=Fellman|first=Megan|date=17 October 2011|work=News|publisher=Northwestern University|accessdate=18 March 2014|location=Evanston, Illinois|archive-date=2015-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151221081528/http://www.northwestern.edu/newscenter/stories/2011/10/blue-stragglers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。目前，在這個星團中已經發現4顆這種恆星<ref>{{cite journal|author=Ahumada, J. A. |author2=Lapasset, E.|date=2007|title=New catalogue of blue stragglers in open clusters|journal= [[Astronomy_and_Astrophysics|Astronomy and Astrophysics]]|volume=463|issue=2|pages=789–97|bibcode=2007A&A...463..789A|doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20054590 }}</ref>。瑞士天文學家Jean-Claude Mermilliod和[[Michel_Mayor|Michel Mayor]]分析這個星團中已經發展成為[[紅巨星|紅巨星]]中質量最小的那些恆星 －1.8至1.9太陽質量的恆星，測量出這個星團的年齡為22億<ref name="Mermilliod">{{cite journal |author=Mermilliod, Jean-Claude |author2=Mayor, Michel |date=1990 |title=Red Giants in Open Clusters. III - Binarity and Stellar Evolution in Five Intermediate-age Clusters: NGC 2360, 2423, 5822, 6811, and IC 4756 |journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics |volume=273 |issue=1 |pages=61–72 |url=http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?1990A%26A...237...61M&data_type=PDF_HIGH&whole_paper=YES&type=PRINTER&filetype=.pdf |bibcode=1990A&A...237...61M |access-date=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2017-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170226222802/http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?1990A%26A...237...61M&data_type=PDF_HIGH&whole_paper=YES&type=PRINTER&filetype=.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這個星團的直徑約為15光年，距離地球3,700光年<ref name="o'meara"/>。

